PREFIX c           - new window
PREFIX ,           - rename window
PREFIX f           - find window
PREFIX n           - next window
PREFIX p           - previous window
PREFIX &           - kill window
PREFIX z           - maximize pane (zoom)
PREFIX +           - Break pane to window
PREFIX -           - Restore pane from window
PREFIX q           - Show pane numbers
PREFIX C-h, C-j... - Resize pane
PREFIX [           - Enter scroll mode
PREFIX w           - List windows
PREFIX x           - Kill pane
PREFIX $           - Rename current session
PREFIX ( or )	   - Previous / next session
PREFIX s           - Choose session from list
PREFIX L           - last session
PREFIX d           - detach from current session
Attach to a session: tmux attach
To get custom layouts for tmuxinator: tmux list-windows
PREFIX o           - Open file / link
PREFIX C-o         - Open file with editor
PREFIX C-I         - Install plugins
